<li>
<strong>Durable, plastic-free storage:</strong> Comes in a sturdy, reusable container for easy clean-up and tidy storage.</li>
<li>
<strong>Supports early development:</strong> Encourages hand-eye coordination, confidence, and creative discovery from the very first stroke.</li>
