<strong>Dimensions: </strong>Each brush and container measures 5.3 × 5.3 × 13.97 cm.</li>
<li>
<strong>Handcrafted by families, for families:</strong> At Honeysticks, we believe in a better way to play – safe, sustainable, and inspiring creativity from the very first moment.</li>
